Text.SourceString: Goomgoom, Hooman. Good it is that you can see us. Need your help freeing the others we will.
Text.LocalizedString: Goomgoom, Hooman. Good it is that you can see us. Need your help freeing the others we will.

Text.SourceString: Goomgoom, hooman. Again we meet.
Text.LocalizedString: Goomgoom, hooman. Again we meet.

Text.SourceString: You the giants thank. Free again we are. Help Hooman we can.
Text.LocalizedString: You the giants thank. Free again we are. Help Hooman we can.

Text.SourceString: Happy again the giants are. Imprisoned no longer we are.
Text.LocalizedString: Happy again the giants are. Imprisoned no longer we are.

Text.SourceString: Strong and healthy again, the island is. Hooman we thank.
Text.LocalizedString: Strong and healthy again, the island is. Hooman we thank.

Text.SourceString: Worried we were for the island. Invisible we are to other hoomans.//But with you, not so. Special one, you are.
Text.LocalizedString: Worried we were for the island. Invisible we are to other hoomans.//But with you, not so. Special one, you are.

Text.SourceString: Hope almost we lost. <NPCName>Goddess</> we thank for your appearance.//Imprisoned no longer, we are.
Text.LocalizedString: Hope almost we lost. <NPCName>Goddess</> we thank for your appearance.//Imprisoned no longer, we are.

Text.SourceString: Unruly the giants can be, but well-meaning they always are. Patience hooman must have.
Text.LocalizedString: Unruly the giants can be, but well-meaning they always are. Patience hooman must have.

Text.SourceString: Today, nice is the air. Very nice.//Falling Season.
Text.LocalizedString: Today, nice is the air. Very nice.//Falling Season.

Text.SourceString: Today, nice is the air. Very nice.//Sprouting Season.
Text.LocalizedString: Today, nice is the air. Very nice.//Sprouting Season.

Text.SourceString: Good day for farming, this is. Busy you must be.
Text.LocalizedString: Good day for farming, this is. Busy you must be.

Text.SourceString: Miss the snow, we do not. Nice and warm Sprouting Season is.
Text.LocalizedString: Miss the snow, we do not. Nice and warm Sprouting Season is.

Text.SourceString: If Hooman looking for bamboo shoots, plenty there are at this time.
Text.LocalizedString: If Hooman looking for bamboo shoots, plenty there are at this time.

Text.SourceString: Looking for kale is Hooman? Plenty around, there should be now.
Text.LocalizedString: Looking for kale is Hooman? Plenty around, there should be now.

Text.SourceString: Looking for wasabi is Hooman? Plenty around, there should be now.
Text.LocalizedString: Looking for wasabi is Hooman? Plenty around, there should be now.

Text.SourceString: If Hooman looking for matsutake, plenty there are at this time.
Text.LocalizedString: If Hooman looking for matsutake, plenty there are at this time.

Text.SourceString: Looking for fig is Hooman? Plenty around, there should be now.
Text.LocalizedString: Looking for fig is Hooman? Plenty around, there should be now.

Text.SourceString: Nice, this rain is. Water all the plants and give animals drink it does.
Text.LocalizedString: Nice, this rain is. Water all the plants and give animals drink it does.

Text.SourceString: Pink, some trees are. Others are green. Nice to see.
Text.LocalizedString: Pink, some trees are. Others are green. Nice to see.

Text.SourceString: Love Sprouting Season, the giants do. More lively we are.//Very nice the sun is on our skin.
Text.LocalizedString: Love Sprouting Season, the giants do. More lively we are.//Very nice the sun is on our skin.

Text.SourceString: Listen to forest song, you must.//Close your eyes. Embrace.
Text.LocalizedString: Listen to forest song, you must.//Close your eyes. Embrace.

Text.SourceString: Plenty of flowers around.//Earth is smiling, it is.
Text.LocalizedString: Plenty of flowers around.//Earth is smiling, it is.

Text.SourceString: Giants purpose is to take care of Earth, goomgoom.//Earth up top, down below and beyond.
Text.LocalizedString: Giants purpose is to take care of Earth, goomgoom.//Earth up top, down below and beyond.

Text.SourceString: The Falling Season, it is.//The season of abundance food.
Text.LocalizedString: The Falling Season, it is.//The season of abundance food.

Text.SourceString: Nature healing. Greatful, we are for the rain.
Text.LocalizedString: Nature healing. Greatful, we are for the rain.

Text.SourceString: Blessing, many forms it come in.//Rain is one of them.
Text.LocalizedString: Blessing, many forms it come in.//Rain is one of them.

Text.SourceString: Nature healing. Greatful, we are for the rain.
Text.LocalizedString: Nature healing. Greatful, we are for the rain.

Text.SourceString: Blessing, many forms it come in.//Rain is one of them.
Text.LocalizedString: Blessing, many forms it come in.//Rain is one of them.

Text.SourceString: Love the rain we do, but take a break from it we must.//Take shelter here, we do.
Text.LocalizedString: Love the rain we do, but take a break from it we must.//Take shelter here, we do.

Text.SourceString: Ice Season is sleeping time.//Sleep, sweet Earth, sleep.
Text.LocalizedString: Ice Season is sleeping time.//Sleep, sweet Earth, sleep.

Text.SourceString: Come to forest, you are...//Hooman, rest.
Text.LocalizedString: Come to forest, you are...//Hooman, rest.

Text.SourceString: Look back, Hooman.//We are watching Sprouting Season coming soon. New beginning, it is.
Text.LocalizedString: Look back, Hooman.//We are watching Sprouting Season coming soon. New beginning, it is.

Text.SourceString: Nature is angry, it seems like.//But healing it is. We believe.
Text.LocalizedString: Nature is angry, it seems like.//But healing it is. We believe.

Text.SourceString: Sad we are, when the sky is like this.//Reminds us of the day the Giants turn to stone, it does.//Goom...
Text.LocalizedString: Sad we are, when the sky is like this.//Reminds us of the day the Giants turn to stone, it does.//Goom...

Text.SourceString: Many moons ago Giants built these houses.//Kept the houses good we did. Wanted it to be good for when the others are back, we did.
Text.LocalizedString: Many moons ago Giants built these houses.//Kept the houses good we did. Wanted it to be good for when the others are back, we did.

Text.SourceString: We enchant tools in center temple.//Giants magic connect to Earth, it does.
Text.LocalizedString: We enchant tools in center temple.//Giants magic connect to Earth, it does.

Text.SourceString: When all Giants gather, our magic is more powerful.//Strong together, we are.
Text.LocalizedString: When all Giants gather, our magic is more powerful.//Strong together, we are.

Text.SourceString: Good listener <NPCName>Grog</> is.//Easy to lead to right direction. Others...worry we do.
Text.LocalizedString: Good listener <NPCName>Grog</> is.//Easy to lead to right direction. Others...worry we do.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Gort</>, sad we are when remember.//Studied hardest, that one. <NPCName>Gort</> is a determined Giant...acomplished great things, <NPCName>Gort</> did.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Gort</>, sad we are when remember.//Studied hardest, that one. <NPCName>Gort</> is a determined Giant...acomplished great things, <NPCName>Gort</> did.

Text.SourceString: Not all great things are good, we must remember.
Text.LocalizedString: Not all great things are good, we must remember.

Text.SourceString: Giants...we all family, goom.//Forgiveness come, it must. Hatred can not win.
Text.LocalizedString: Giants...we all family, goom.//Forgiveness come, it must. Hatred can not win.

Text.SourceString: Hate family, we do not.//We love family... Embrace family, we must.
Text.LocalizedString: Hate family, we do not.//We love family... Embrace family, we must.

Text.SourceString: Hatred kill love, Hooman.//Remove hate from heart, we must. Heart only for love.
Text.LocalizedString: Hatred kill love, Hooman.//Remove hate from heart, we must. Heart only for love.

Text.SourceString: We love and love will come.//Do not ask, love who. Love all, we do.
Text.LocalizedString: We love and love will come.//Do not ask, love who. Love all, we do.

Text.SourceString: Powerful water Giant <NPCName>Gong</> is. Match <NPCName>Gong</> we cannot.
Text.LocalizedString: Powerful water Giant <NPCName>Gong</> is. Match <NPCName>Gong</> we cannot.

Text.SourceString: Poison, jealousy is goomgoom.//It break Giants. It breaks Hooman. Poison, jealousy is.
Text.LocalizedString: Poison, jealousy is goomgoom.//It break Giants. It breaks Hooman. Poison, jealousy is.

Text.SourceString: Cleanse your heart, Hooman.//Our loved ones, we must focus on.
Text.LocalizedString: Cleanse your heart, Hooman.//Our loved ones, we must focus on.

Text.SourceString: Happy, we are.
Text.LocalizedString: Happy, we are.

Text.SourceString: Each Giant can enchant tools, goom//Talk to Giant, you must.
Text.LocalizedString: Each Giant can enchant tools, goom//Talk to Giant, you must.

Text.SourceString: The way to find out is to find out.
Text.LocalizedString: The way to find out is to find out.

Text.SourceString: Be bad at things, do not. That is key to success.
Text.LocalizedString: Be bad at things, do not. That is key to success.

Text.SourceString: Casting magic is how Giants enchant tools.
Text.LocalizedString: Casting magic is how Giants enchant tools.
